&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is both a strong people leader and a modern operator — someone who can leverage data, technology, AI tools, and process improvements to increase the effectiveness and productivity of the BDR function while maintaining a high-performing, human-centered sales culture. We are searching for someone who is excited about using emerging technologies to augment the human side of outbound sales and relationship-building.&lt;/p&gt;
