&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute outbound sales and marketing strategies to generate high-quality leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Marketing to support campaign execution, lead follow-up, event outreach, content promotion, and demand generation initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Marketing, Sales, and Revenue Operations to ensure alignment on target markets, messaging, lead quality, reporting, and pipeline goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and track team KPIs, providing feedback and coaching to improve performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct performance reviews, provide training, and create development plans for team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage HubSpot CRM to ensure effective lead tracking, follow-ups, and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze sales, campaign, and performance data to identify trends and opportunities for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously improve outbound prospecting methods (email, phone, social outreach) and optimize workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI tools, automation platforms, and modern sales technologies to improve prospecting efficiency, personalization, research, reporting, and overall BDR productivity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate, test, and implement new tools and workflows that help scale outbound efforts while improving the quality and relevance of human interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data and technology to help the BDR team prioritize accounts, identify buying signals, personalize outreach, and improve conversion rates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay informed on industry trends, emerging technologies, and best practices in sales development to keep the team competitive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to overall company growth by identifying opportunities for scaling the business development function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
